data.description: NEW & IMPROVED PRICE!!  Beautifully maintained home on over 1/2 acre in Arden.  This 3/4 bedroom, 3 full bath home sits on a private, wooded lot.  Meticulously kept and improved by the owner, this home is sure to impress with vaulted ceilings in the main living area, a deck off the dining room, and an oversized one-car garage.  The water treatment system was installed in 2009 with a new neutralizer in 2018.  Rheem lifetime warranty 50-gallon hot water heater was installed in 2014.  The insulated garage door was installed in 2017.  Trane 16 SEER HVAC indoor and outdoor units were installed in 2018.  Architectural shingle roof less than ten years old.  The primary bath was renovated with a whirlpool/jacuzzi tub, custom vanity, and cabinet in 2012.  The house has the electric wiring for an electric car / Tesla charging station.  The lower level family room could easily be used as a huge primary suite / 4th bedroom.  Enjoy the incredible water access that Arden offers including several community beaches, kayak and canoe launches, pavilions, playgrounds, and more.
